    "title": "瑪拉基書 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>耶和華（雅巍）的話是藉著誰傳給以色列的？</strong></p><p>耶和華（雅巍）的話是藉著瑪拉基傳給以色列的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:1",
          "end_ref": "39001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614423,
    "reference_id": 129313,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 1:2–3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39001002-39001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>耶和華（雅巍）愛誰，惡誰？</strong></p><p>耶和華（雅巍）愛以色列，愛雅各，惡以掃。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:2",
          "end_ref": "39001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614424,
    "reference_id": 129314,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 1:4–5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39001004-39001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>當耶和華（雅巍）</strong><span><strong>拆毀</strong></span><strong>以東人</strong><span><strong>重建的荒廢之處</strong></span><strong>時，以色列會有何回應？</strong></p><p>以色列要回應說：「<span>願耶和華（雅巍）在以色列境界之外被尊為大。</span>」</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:4",
          "end_ref": "39001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614425,
    "reference_id": 129315,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 1:6–7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39001006-39001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>作為以色列的父親和主人，耶和華（雅巍）問了祭司什麼？</strong></p><p>耶和華（雅巍）問祭司，祂的名應得的<span>尊敬</span>和<span>敬畏</span>在哪裡，且為什麼他們藐視祂的名和祂的桌子。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39001006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:6",
          "end_ref": "39001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614426,
    "reference_id": 129316,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 1:8–9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39001008-39001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>耶和華（雅巍）會如何回應那些瞎眼的、瘸腿的和有病的祭物？</strong></p><p>耶和華（雅巍）不會悅納瞎眼的、瘸腿的和有病的祭物，也不會因這些祭物施恩給以色列，更不會因他們獻上這些祭物而接納以色列。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:8",
          "end_ref": "39001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614427,
    "reference_id": 129317,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 1:10–11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39001010-39001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼耶和華（雅巍）願以色列人中間有人關上聖殿的門，免得他們徒然在祂的壇上燒火？</strong></p><p>因為耶和華（雅巍）的名在列國中<span>必尊為大</span>，在各處，列國將獻上<span>潔淨的供物</span>，與以色列人所獻的供物不同。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39001010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:10",
          "end_ref": "39001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614428,
    "reference_id": 129318,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 1:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39001013",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>祭司如何看待關於那耶和華（雅巍）的事奉？</strong></p><p>他們認為<span>這些事很煩瑣</span>，並且輕蔑地嗤之以鼻。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39001013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:13",
          "end_ref": "39001013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614429,
    "reference_id": 129319,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 1:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼主要咒詛那些發誓要用羊</strong><span><strong>羣</strong></span><strong>中的公牲畜獻祭，卻獻上</strong><span><strong>有殘疾</strong></span><strong>的牲畜的欺騙者？</strong></p><p>因為耶和華（雅巍）是大君王，祂的名<span>在列國中是可畏的。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:14",
          "end_ref": "39001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614430,
    "reference_id": 129320,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:3–4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002003-39002004",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>祭司是如何知道耶和華（雅巍）命令他們要將榮耀歸給祂的名的？</strong></p><p>他們是藉著耶和華（雅巍）<span>使他們的福分變為咒詛</span>，並且<span>把糞抹在他們的臉上而</span>知道的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:3",
          "end_ref": "39002004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614431,
    "reference_id": 129321,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002007",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼利未要尊敬耶和華（雅巍），敬畏耶和華的名，口中有真實的教訓而非不義，與耶和華同行在平安和正直，並使許多人離開罪惡？</strong></p><p>因為祭司是耶和華（雅巍）的使者，當存知識。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:7",
          "end_ref": "39002007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614432,
    "reference_id": 129322,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:8–9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002008-39002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>祭司是如何敗壞利未的約並不遵守耶和華（雅巍）的道？</strong></p><p>祭司在教導上<span>偏離了正道</span>，因此敗壞了這約。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:8",
          "end_ref": "39002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614433,
    "reference_id": 129323,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:10–12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002010-39002012",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>耶和華（雅巍）要從雅各的</strong><span><strong>帳棚</strong></span><strong>中</strong><span><strong>剪除</strong></span><strong>誰？</strong></p><p>耶和華（雅巍）要剪除那些對弟兄詭詐行事，以及娶事奉外邦神的女子為妻，又向耶和華獻供物的人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:10",
          "end_ref": "39002012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614434,
    "reference_id": 129324,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:14–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002014-39002015",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼耶和華（雅巍）不接受以色列的供物？</strong></p><p>因為以色列人對他們年輕時<span>所娶的</span>妻子不忠誠。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:14",
          "end_ref": "39002015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614435,
    "reference_id": 129325,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:15–16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002015-39002016",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>耶和華（雅巍）為什麼命令以色列人要謹守自己的心，不可行詭詐？</strong></p><p>因為耶和華（雅巍）使以色列人和他的妻子成為一體，<span>為了使人</span>得虔誠的後裔；並且耶和華恨惡休妻的事和以強暴待妻的人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:15",
          "end_ref": "39002016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614436,
    "reference_id": 129326,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 2:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>以色列人如何用他們的</strong><span><strong>言語使</strong></span><strong>耶和華（雅巍）厭煩？</strong></p><p>他們用他們的言語使耶和華（雅巍）厭煩，因為他們說行惡的人在耶和華眼中看為善，並且祂喜悅他們，又問公義的神在哪裡。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39002017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:17",
          "end_ref": "39002017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 2:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614437,
    "reference_id": 129327,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003001",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>當耶和華（雅巍）差遣為祂預備道路的使者來後，會發生什麼事？</strong></p><p>以色列所尋求的主會<span>忽然</span>進入祂的殿。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:1",
          "end_ref": "39003001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614438,
    "reference_id": 129328,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003003",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>猶大和耶路撒冷</strong><span><strong>所獻的</strong></span><strong>供物何時會蒙耶和華（雅巍）的</strong><span><strong>悅納</strong></span><strong>？</strong></p><p>當利未的子孫被<span>潔淨</span>，<span>熬煉他們像金銀一樣</span>，猶大和耶路撒冷所獻的供物就會蒙耶和華（雅巍）悅納。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:3",
          "end_ref": "39003003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614439,
    "reference_id": 129329,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:4–5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003004-39003005",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>在利未的子孫被潔淨後，猶大和耶路撒冷</strong><span><strong>的</strong></span><strong>供物</strong><span><strong>蒙</strong></span><strong>耶和華（雅巍）</strong><span><strong>悅納</strong></span><strong>，耶和華會做什麼事？</strong></p><p>祂必<span>臨近</span>以色列，施行審判，並迅速作見證攻擊那些不<span>敬畏祂的</span>人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:4",
          "end_ref": "39003005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614440,
    "reference_id": 129330,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:6–7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003006-39003007",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>即使雅各的子孫偏離了耶和華（雅巍）的律例，為什麼他們沒有被消滅？</strong></p><p>他們<span>沒有被</span>消滅，因為耶和華（雅巍）是不改變的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:6",
          "end_ref": "39003007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614441,
    "reference_id": 129331,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003007",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>以色列是如何</strong><span><strong>偏離</strong></span><strong>耶和華（雅巍）的？</strong></p><p>他們因不遵守祂的典章而偏離了祂。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:7",
          "end_ref": "39003007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614442,
    "reference_id": 129332,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>以色列是如何</strong><span><strong>搶奪</strong></span><strong>神的？</strong></p><p>他們在<span>十分之一奉獻和供物上</span>搶奪了神。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:8",
          "end_ref": "39003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614443,
    "reference_id": 129333,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:10–12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003010-39003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>耶和華（雅巍）應許，如果以色列人將當納的十分之一全然送入倉庫，會發生什麼事？</strong></p><p>耶和華（雅巍）應許祂必斥責<span>蝗蟲</span>，並且萬國必稱以色列為有福的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:10",
          "end_ref": "39003012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614444,
    "reference_id": 129334,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:13–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003013-39003015",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>以色列人</strong><span><strong>用甚麼話</strong></span><strong>頂撞了耶和華（雅巍）？</strong></p><p>他們說事奉神是徒然的，因為那些狂傲的人和行惡的人雖然試探神，卻仍然<span>得以建立</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:13",
          "end_ref": "39003015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 614445,
    "reference_id": 129335,
    "version": "1.0.1",
    "title": "瑪拉基書 3:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "39003017",
    "language": "zht",
    "review_level": "None",
    "content": "<p><strong>耶和華（雅巍）說誰將屬於祂並得到</strong><span><strong>憐恤</strong></span><strong>？</strong></p><p>耶和華（雅巍）說，那些敬畏祂、<span>思念</span>祂名的人將屬於祂，並得到憐恤。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "39003017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:17",
          "end_ref": "39003017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "MAL 3:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
